          [Psycojoker]
        
        - Wrap sys.excepthook only once.
          [marciomazza]
        
        - Add GPL file and refer in headers.
          [stan3]
        
        - Python 3 support.
          [Piet Delport]
        
        - Basic tests.
          [msabramo]
        
        - Added the functions ``runcall``, ``runeval`` and ``run``.
          [dimasad]
        
        
        0.6.1 (2011-10-17)
        ------------------
        
        - State dependency on IPython later or equal to 0.10.
          [gotcha]
        
        
        0.6 (2011-09-01)
